feedback_meta.text:
-= Kitchen =-
You arrive in a kitchen. An usual kind of place. I guess you better just go and list everything you see here.

You see a gleam over in a corner, where you can see a fridge. Huh, weird. The fridge contains a red onion and a cilantro. I mean, just wow! Isn't TextWorld just the best? You scan the room for an oven, and you find an oven. An oven... Is that really what you were looking for? As if things weren't amazing enough already, you can even see a table. Make a note of this, you might have to put stuff on or in it later on. The table is massive. On the table you can see a knife. You scan the room for a counter, and you find a counter. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it. You see a gleam over in a corner, where you can see a stove. Make a note of this, you might have to put stuff on or in it later on. But the thing is empty.

There is an open plain door leading east. There is an exit to the south. There is an exit to the west.
